quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,34,"(Tachisalilidwa yanti): “Jijinjilani (Mbepojo) mwantendele. Ali ni lisiku lya umi wandamo.”"
  50,35,"Akwete kupata ŵanganyao chilichose chatakachisacheje mwalakwemo, soni Kukwetu kwana yakonjechesya (kum’bona Allah)."
  50,36,"Ana mikutula jilingwa jatwajijonasile paujo pao, ŵaŵaliji ŵamachili nnope kwapunda ŵanganyaŵa, nambo soni ŵasyungwile-syungwile mu ilambo, ana ni ŵapapatile pakutilila (ndema ja yaichilile ipotesi, ngati ŵajonasiche)?"
  51,28,"Basi ni wampatile woga wakwajogopa ŵanganyao. Ŵanyao ŵatite: “Nkajogopa.” Ni ŵampele abali jakusengwasya janti chakole mwanache jwakumanyilila nnope."
  51,29,"Ni ŵayiche ŵankwakwe (ŵali Sara) ni masegwe, aku ali nkuliputa kungope (ligongo lya usimongo), ni ŵatite: “Jwanchekulupe, jwampalale (timbeleche chinauli)!”"
  51,30,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Iyyoyopeyo (tim’beleche mwam’belelemo), Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) niyatite, chisimu Ŵalakweo ni Ŵalunda lwakusokoka, Ŵakumanyilila nnope.”"
  52,19,"(Tachasalila kuti): “Lyagani soni mwagani mwakusengwa ligongo lya ayila (yambone) yamwaliji nkutenda.”"
  52,20,"Ali ajegeme mu itengu yauchimbichimbi yejalidwe chenene, ni tuchalombekasya ni achimmasyeto ŵameso gakulanguka soni gekulungwa mwakusalalila."
  52,21,"Sano aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kwaakuuya ŵanache ŵao pa chikulupi, chitukasimanganye ŵanganyao ni ŵanache ŵao, soni ngatuja kwapunguchisya (malipilo ga) masengo gao chilichose. Mundu jwalijose tachiŵa uwombosi wakuliombolela ku (yakusakala) yaŵapanganyisye (pakutaŵidwa ku Moto)."
  53,13,"Soni chisimu (Muhammadi ﷺ) ŵam’bweni (Jibulilu) ndema jine (chilo cha Al-Mi‘râj)."
  53,14,"Pa chitela chansaawu chakupelelapo (indu yakwela kwinani kapena kutuluka pasi, chachili kusyeto kwa mawunde nsano nagaŵili)."
  53,15,"Palakwepo ni pajili Mbepo Jakutamilichikamo."
  54,4,"Soni chisimu chene pamasile pasyaayiiche ŵanganyao ngani (mu aji Qur’an) syasikwete nkati mwakwe ikaanyo yaukali (yakwakanya kutenda yakusakala)."
  54,5,"(Aji Qur’an jiŵele jegumbale) lunda lwakusokoka nnope, nambo itetelo ya akutetela nganiyiŵa ikamuchisye (kwa ŵandu ŵaajitundumalile)."
  54,6,"Basi mwalekani. (Mwakumbusyani) lisiku lyatachiŵilanga nkuŵilanga (Israfil) ku chindu chakunyalaya kusyene (chiŵalanjilo cha pa Kiyama)."